Reference a message key, defined in your messages module corresponding to the current locale.

{{format-message
    messageKey='product.info'
    product='Apple watch'
    price=200
    deadline=yesterday}}

Passing a static message or a message via a data-binding also works.

{{format-message
    message=messages.photos
    name='Jason'
    numPhotos=photosTaken
    takenDate=yesterday}}